Heat sugar and cayenne pepper in medium skillet until melted. Toss in pecans. Spread pecans on waxed paper; cool. Prepare grill to medium heat. Lightly spray plums with olive oil cooking spray; salt and pepper to taste. Grill until slightly soft, turning once (about 6-8 minutes). Set aside. Toss salad greens with dressing. Divide among 4 salad plates. Top with plum slices and sprinkle with cheese and pecans.